[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "レスナちゃん、素材用意しといたよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_036_00000",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "うん、ありがとう",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_00001",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（私たちは果ての大陸に向かうため、北の果てにある\n　暗黒の氷海に挑戦した）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_00002",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（結果は……ダメだった。大量の頂獣級の魔物が\n　出現し、私たちは撤退することしかできなかった）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_00003",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（でも、そこで「九偉人図」という絵画を\n　見つけることができた）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_00004",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（この「九偉人図」が九枚揃うことで、\n　果ての大陸への道が開ける、らしいんだけど……）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_00005",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "レスナちゃん、かき混ぜすぎじゃない？\nハンマーもそう言ってるよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_036_00006",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "え？　わわっ！\nき、危機一髪……ありがと、イザナちゃん",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_00007",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "どうしたの？　考えごとしてた？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_036_00008",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "「九偉人図」のこと。集められるのかなあって",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_00009",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "暗黒の氷海で１枚、ケイウンの宝物庫で１枚、\nそれにアルビーナが１枚見つけてくれたよね？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_036_00010",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "うん、あと６枚。それと……アルビーナのこともかな。\nできれば、もっと安心させてあげたくて",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_00011",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "暗黒の氷海のことで、かなり落ち込んでたもんね。\n少し元気になったみたいだけど……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_036_00012",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "次に行くブラオールは無数島群域でも\n一番大きな街だし、安全なんでしょ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_036_00013",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "うん、危険はないと思う。ケイウンに「九偉人図」を\n寄贈したっていう、有力者の方を訪ねるだけだから",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_00014",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "もし何かあっても\nイザナちゃんやヨハナちゃんが……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_00015",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "377912885312431765",
		"text": "残念だけど今回は私、一緒に行けないの",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_036_00016",
		"still_path_hash": "6764252557264005345",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "あれ、そうなの？　どうして？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_036_00017",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "377912885312431765",
		"text": "おじいちゃんの裁判が始まるのよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_036_00018",
		"still_path_hash": "6764252557264005345",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "ヨハナちゃんのおじいちゃん……\n月影の会のオリバーさんだね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_00019",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "377912885312431765",
		"text": "うん。月影の会はみんなに悪いことをした。\nだから……私も一緒に謝るの",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_036_00020",
		"still_path_hash": "6764252557264005345",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（ヨハナちゃんは元々、月影の会という\n　王国非公認組織の監視役で、そこの会長のお孫さん）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_00021",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（でも、この子ならきっとやり直せると思って\n　私はヨハナちゃんを引き取ると決めた）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_00022",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "377912885312431765",
		"text": "おじいちゃんは私は出廷する必要ないって言うけど……\n謝って済む問題じゃないけど",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_036_00023",
		"still_path_hash": "6764252557264005345",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "377912885312431765",
		"text": "でも……やっぱり謝らなきゃいけないと思う",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_036_00024",
		"still_path_hash": "6764252557264005345",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "377912885312431765",
		"text": "レスナたちと冒険するようになって、色々なことを\n学んで、どれだけ酷いことをしていたか分かった",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_036_00025",
		"still_path_hash": "6764252557264005345",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "377912885312431765",
		"text": "ちゃんと向き合って、戻ってくるから。\nだから少しだけ、お別れよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_036_00026",
		"still_path_hash": "6764252557264005345",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "分かった。ヨハナちゃんがそうしたいって\n自分で決めたんだもんね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_00027",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "そういうことなら……しょうがないよね。\nブラオールはアタシに任せて！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_036_00028",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "殿下やユナさんもしばらく王都に\nいる必要があるって話だったから",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_036_00029",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "アタシが騎士として、みんなをしっかり守っちゃうよ。\nこのハンマーにかけて！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_036_00030",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "あはは、剣じゃなくてハンマーなの\nイザナちゃんらしくて頼もしいな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_00031",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "うん、ブラオールでもよろしくね！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_00032",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]